Before anyone joins:

/gamerule spawnRadius 0

After everyone joins:

/give @a minecraft:bow{Unbreakable:1,Enchantments:[{id:power,lvl:100000}, {id:infinity,lvl:1}]}
/effect give @a minecraft:mining_fatigue 999999 8 true
/effect give @a minecraft:regeneration 1000000 255 true
/effect give @a minecraft:saturation 1000000 255 true
/give @a minecraft:arrow
/effect give @a minecraft:invisibility 1000000 0 true
/give @a minecraft:ender_pearl 5

After everyone hides:

/item replace entity @a armor.head with minecraft:golden_helmet{Unbreakable:1,Enchantments:[{id:binding_curse,lvl:1}]}
/item replace entity @a armor.chest with minecraft:golden_chestplate{Unbreakable:1,Enchantments:[{id:binding_curse,lvl:1}]}
/item replace entity @a armor.feet with minecraft:golden_boots{Unbreakable:1,Enchantments:[{id:binding_curse,lvl:1}]}
/item replace entity @a armor.legs with minecraft:golden_leggings{Unbreakable:1,Enchantments:[{id:binding_curse,lvl:1}]}
